%% Diagram: Multi-tier cache hierarchy for paste reads
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    USER["Reader"]
    CDN["CDN edge<br/>TTL 300s · ~5 ms"]
    REDIS["Redis cluster<br/>TTL 1h · ~1 ms"]
    PG[("PostgreSQL<br/>metadata · ~5 ms")]
    S3["Object storage<br/>compressed body · ~30 ms"]

    USER --> CDN
    CDN -->|miss| REDIS
    REDIS -->|miss| PG
    PG --> S3
    S3 -->|decompress + populate| REDIS
    REDIS -->|response + populate| CDN
    CDN -->|response| USER
